{
  "stem": "19939.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 94.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was such a shame to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how I was-- is for the psychologist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They talk about it, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the victim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I can go on a little faster.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went to-- they took me to a displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Landeck.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was mainly--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Austria.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was mainly for Eastern European, Slavic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there were Yugoslavians, Russians, Hungarian, Polish, a lot of Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that camp, I was-- you know, one of the, the men that worked in this village was a former teacher from Gdansk or something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he knew other people that were in the camp, prince, former.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of Polish people that were sent away from Warsaw when they had the, the uprising.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this intelligentsia, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got into this through him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- what, the priest were came there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The priest from-- came from the camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I worked as a priest's secretary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was taking different kinds of-- there were former, you know, officers from camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were giving lessons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How long were you there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there a few months, probably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all through this time, this Lambert or his sister were coming and bringing me, helping bringing me food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was just like a sister to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then from there, I went to Haiming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, the food was already, you know-- the [INAUDIBLE] for the [INAUDIBLE] camps-- the food was not sufficient, I mean, for-- because I got the boils on my hands.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're giving us watered spinach soup, piece of bread, or you know, things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was-- then I was-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe this was already in the third camp, in Kufstein.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kufstein was the third camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
